Introduction

Dohu is a South Korean singer-songwriter and producer. He made his solo debut under INOFF MUSIC on November 7, 2018, with the digital single "Savior". He was a top 16 contestant on the 2019 Channel A survival show "Vocal Play 2". He was announced as a new artist of MECHIVE on July 19, 2021.
